Intent
    Define a interface for creating an object, but let subclasses decide which class to instantiate.

Factory Method lets a class defer instantiation to subclasses.
    Bir sinifin nesne olusturmasini alt siniflara otelenmesine izin verir.

   Creation of an object is an important thing in oop. There are a lot of classes that has their own complexities
   they are created in many places in an project.


  Nesnelerin nerede olusturulacagi problemini cozer.
  Nesnelerin olusturulmasini soyutlar ve bu isi istemci kodlarindan cikarip factory metotlara havale eder.

  Bir interface de tanimlanir ve alt siniflarda gerceklestierilir.